Parliament, Monday, 6 March 2023 – The Portfolio Committee on Higher Education, Science and Innovation will tomorrow convene an urgent meeting for briefings by the South African Union of Students and the South Africa Technical and Vocational Education and Training Students Association on developments at universities and TVET colleges.
	
	Details of the meeting are as follows;
	
	Date: Tuesday, 7 March 2023
	Time: 09:00
	Venue: Virtual Platform
	
	Members of the media who wish to observe the Parliament sittings on a virtual platform should forward their contact details to Mr Mlindi Mpindi at mmpindi@parliament.gov.za for inclusion in the Parliament Communications Service WhatsApp group, where login details will be shared. Journalists must forward their requests using their official email addresses (no private emails).
	
	Members of the public may follow the proceedings live on Parliament TV (DSTV Channel 408), via the live stream on Parliament’s YouTube channel, Facebook and Twitter pages. Please see the links below.
	
	You may subscribe to the Parliament YouTube channel to receive instant notifications of live feeds.
	Twitter: https://twitter.com/ParliamentofRSA
	Facebook: https://facebook.com/ParliamentofRSA
	YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/ParliamentofRSA
	ISSUED BY THE PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES
	
